article.headline: Marshall's double-double powers Santa Clara past Mississippi Valley State 81-39

images.name: Mississippi Valley State Delta Devils vs. Santa Clara Broncos: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Marshall's double-double powers Santa Clara past Mississippi Valley State 81-39
article.story: SANTA CLARA, Calif. -- — Carlos Marshall Jr. scored 14 points and grabbed 12 rebounds as Santa Clara cruised past Mississippi Valley State 81-39 on Monday night. Johnny O'Neil scored 12 points, going 5 of 6 (2 for 3 from 3-point range) for the Broncos (5-0). Christoph Tilly finished 4 of 7 from the field to finish with 10 points. Donovan Sanders finished with 15 points for the Delta Devils (0-5). Walter Hamilton added five points for Mississippi Valley State. Rayquan Brown also put up four points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
